## Why This Is Asked

Observability is critical for CNPA; end-to-end tracing helps identify latency sources across HTTP, DB, and Kafka.

## Key Concepts

- Distributed tracing
- OpenTelemetry SDKs and exporters
- Trace context propagation headers and Kafka headers
- Sampling strategies
- End-to-end verification under load

## Code Example

```javascript
// Node.js OpenTelemetry setup sketch
const tracer = opentelemetry.trace.getTracer('cnpa');
app.use((req, res, next) => {
  const span = tracer.startSpan('http', { attributes: { 'http.method': req.method }});
  res.on('finish', () => span.end());
  next();
});
```

